Object.Field:
Student completed units with advanced standing by course and semester. This is the first stage of the query, the total course units and advanced standing units need to be summed. This will be done in the corresponding interface SIL_T_STU_ADVANCED_STD_I
Ben - 15/6/2017 There was an issue with Load Modelling Progression flag calculations for latest year enrolments. If there was not a record in the advanced standing table for the latest enrolment, then the accumulated units completed and accumulated adbvanced satnding did not sum correctly Needed to add the latest year enrolment and set the competed units to zero for that year so the accumulated totals will add up correctly in the progression flag SQL
